data.description: ** A wonderful opportunity to purchase this home by assuming the remaining $274,000 FHA mortgage at 2.625% and getting a 2nd mortgage with a lender of your choosing for the balance (or paying cash).**  Welcome to this stunning pool home in sought-after neighborhood of Grand Oaks. Located on a large lot with a beautiful water view, this home is sure to impress! This spacious home features 4 bedrooms 2.5 bathrooms and a 2 car garage. Recent improvements include: Roof (2021), HVAC (2020), Pool pump and pool resurface (2022) and high efficiency water heater (2024). Downstairs you will find a formal sitting/living room, formal dining room, open kitchen featuring magnificent granite counters, island, stainless appliances and an OVERSIZED walk in pantry. The kitchen opens to the family room so no one misses the action! Head outside to the backyard oasis, relax in your pool and enjoy the water view or snuggle up with a good book in the screen lanai. Also, there is a low maintenance vinyl fenced yard for the pups!  Upstairs are 3 large secondary bedrooms a second bath and a remarkable master suite offering the utmost relaxation and comfort, with a well-appointed him and her bathroom sink, a tub and separate shower with a massive walk-in closet. Grand Oaks is a well-maintained neighborhood with great amenities including clubhouse, playground, pool, spa, exercise facility, basketball courts and a boardwalk trail. Situated closely to the apex of I-275 and I-75 as well as SR 56 and SR 54, you are within a short drive of shopping at The Grove, Tampa Premium Outlet Mall, Costco, Sam's Club and more. Additionally, hospitals, medical centers, entertainment options like Main Event and PopStroke, and loads of tasty restaurants are close by. Grand Oaks has ZERO CDD and a low monthly HOA of only $105!  Hurry and make this YOUR dream home!
